## PHASE 3 — Hapkonic Admin Portal (Full Control Center)

**Duration:** 5–6 days

- Build admin portal at `/admin` with protected routes (role: `admin`, `manager`)
- **Client Management:**
  - CRUD for clients (company name, logo, industry, contact info)
  - Assign projects to clients
  - Client profile overview: all projects, documents, invoices, activity at a glance
- **User/Credential Management:**
  - Admin creates login credentials for clients (no self-registration)
  - Set roles: `admin`, `manager`, `client`
  - Password generation + secure email delivery of credentials via Resend
  - Force password reset on first login
  - Deactivate/reactivate client accounts
- **Project Management:**
  - Create projects, assign to clients, set date range, description, status
  - Add/edit/reorder milestones and tasks (feeds into Gantt chart + timeline)
  - Set task dependencies, assignees, progress percentages
- **Document Upload Center:**
  - Drag-and-drop multi-file uploader for all 11 document categories
  - Bulk upload with auto-categorization
  - Replace/version existing documents
  - View which documents each client has seen/downloaded
- **Progress Update Publisher:**
  - Rich text editor (Markdown + image embed) to post progress updates per project
  - Attach screenshots, files, or links to each update
  - Set overall project percentage and per-category breakdown
  - Updates appear instantly on client's dashboard
- **Invoice Manager:**
  - Upload PDF invoices per client (via Uploadthing)
  - Set amount, due date, status (`Pending`, `Paid`, `Overdue`, `Partially Paid`)
  - Manually mark invoices as paid/partially paid/write off
  - Add notes to invoices (visible to client)
  - Trigger payment reminder emails manually or via schedule
- **Meeting Scheduler:**
  - Create/edit meetings that sync to Google Calendar
  - Add agenda notes (visible to client before meeting)
  - Post meeting summary + action items after meeting
- **Milestone Comment Inbox:**
  - Unified view of all client comments across all milestones
  - Reply to client comments directly from admin panel
  - Mark conversations as resolved
  - Unread/flagged comment indicators
- **Activity Log:**
  - Full audit trail: who created/modified/deleted what, when
  - Filterable by admin user, action type, date range
  - Export log as CSV

**Deliverable:** A powerful single admin portal where Hapkonic team manages everything — clients, projects, documents, invoices, updates, meetings, and communication.

